d-foreground mb-6\">Trusted by the biggest names in tech — direct relationships at the highest levels</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gold/5 hover:bg-gold/10 border border-gold/10\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark shadow-gold/70 ring-2 ring-gold/20\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold \">Meta Partner</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award inline w-3.5 h-3.5 text-gold ml-1.5 -mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg> <!-- -->— <!-- -->Official Meta partner — flown to Meta HQ, met Mark Zuckerberg, consulted on Quest 3 development, collaborated with Meta AI team on XR innovation</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gold/5 hover:bg-gold/10 border border-gold/10\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark shadow-gold/70 ring-2 ring-gold/20\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold \">Google Partner</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award inline w-3.5 h-3.5 text-gold ml-1.5 -mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.