te-100 to-slate-50 hover:from-slate-200/60 hover:to-slate-100/60 border border-slate-300/60\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-300 via-white to-slate-400 shadow-slate-400/60 ring-2 ring-slate-200\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-slate-700\">NASA Contract (2026)</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-1.5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wide bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-200 to-slate-300 text-slate-600 border border-slate-300/80 -mt-0.5 align-middle\">PLATINUM</span> <!-- -->— <!-- -->Second NASA award/contract — continuing partnership with NASA on advanced space technology systems</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-100 to-slate-50 hover:from-slate-200/60 hover:to-slate-100/60 border border-slate-300/60\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-300 via-white to-slate-400 shadow-slate-400/60 ring-2 ring-slate-200\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-slate-700\">AIRAS Ballistic Missile Defense</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-1.5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wide bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-200 to-slate-300 text-slate-600 border border-slate-300/80 -mt-0.5 align-middle\">PLATINUM</span> <!-- -->— <!-- -->Awarded contract for AI-integrated ballistic missile defense system for U.S. Navy destroyers — advanced threat detection and response architecture</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gold/5 hover:bg-gold/10 border border-gold/10\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark shadow-gold/70 ring-2