cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg> <!-- -->— <!-- -->Proprietary RAG engines, vectorization, LLM pipelines — reusable Background IP deployed across all projects</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gold/5 hover:bg-gold/10 border border-gold/10\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark shadow-gold/70 ring-2 ring-gold/20\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold \">48-Hour MVP Framework</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award inline w-3.5 h-3.5 text-gold ml-1.5 -mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg> <!-- -->— <!-- -->From idea to market in 2 days — proven methodology across 5+ client engagements</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gold/5 hover:bg-gold/10 border border-gold/10\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark shadow-gold/70 ring-2 ring-gold/20\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold \">Web Scraping Framework</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award inline w-3.5 h-3.5 text-gold ml-1.5 -mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg> <!-- -->— <!-- -->Enterprise-grade data collection from county records, satellite imagery, public databases, and web sources</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-default bg-gold/5 hover:bg-gold/10 border border-gold/10\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md flex-none bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark shadow-gold/70 ring-2 ring-gold/20\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"font-semibold \">Computer Vision Pipeline</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award inline w-3.5 h-3.5 text-gold ml-1.5 -mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg> <!-- -->— <!-- -->Image recognition, object detection, and visual AI — deployed in defense and commercial applications</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-6\"><button class=\"magnetic-btn inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground border border-gold/20 hover:border-gold/40 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-gold/5\">See All 6<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"py-24 scroll-mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"transition-all duration-700 ease-out opacity-0 translate-y-8 \" style=\"transition-delay:0ms\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4\"><span class=\"gold-shimmer-text\">Ready to Build?</span></h2><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Let&#x27;s discuss how we can architect your next strategic advantage. Start with a<!-- --> <span class=\"gold-gradient-text font-semibold\">free</span> <!-- -->consultation.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"transition-all duration-700 ease-out opacity-0 -translate-x-8 \" style=\"transition-delay:100ms\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border p-8 shadow-sm\"><form class=\"space-y-4\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Send Us a Message</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4\">Tell us about your project and we&#x27;ll respond within 24 hours.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground mb-1.5\">Name *</label><input id=\"name\" type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-border bg-white text-foreground text-sm placeholder:text-muted-foreground/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/40 focus:border-gold transition-all\" placeholder=\"Your name\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground mb-1.5\">Email *</label><input id=\"email\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-border bg-white text-foreground text-sm placeholder:text-muted-foreground/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/40 focus:border-gold transition-all\" placeholder=\"you@company.com\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div><label for=\"company\" class=\"block text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground mb-1.5\">Company</label><input id=\"company\" type=\"text\" class=\"w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-border bg-white text-foreground text-sm placeholder:text-muted-foreground/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/40 focus:border-gold transition-all\" placeholder=\"Your company (optional)\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground mb-1.5\">Message *</label><textarea id=\"message\" required=\"\" rows=\"4\" class=\"w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-border bg-white text-foreground text-sm placeholder:text-muted-foreground/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/40 focus:border-gold transition-all resize-none\" placeholder=\"Tell us about your project, industry, and what you&#x27;re looking to build...\"></textarea></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"magnetic-btn glass-btn w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-transparent backdrop-blur-md text-foreground border border-foreground/30 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-60 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg>Send Message</button></form></div></div><div class=\"transition-all duration-700 ease-out opacity-0 translate-x-8 \" style=\"transition-delay:200ms\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\"><div class=\"tilt-card bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/60 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-foreground/5 flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5 border border-foreground/10\"><svg xmlns=\"h